orb1_sclkscet_[0-9]{5}.tsc.description: This file is a SPICE spacecraft clock (SCLK) kernel containing information required for M01 spacecraft on-board clock to UTC conversion.

m01_hga_ext[0-9]{2}.bc.description: This file contains orientation and angular rate data for the Mars'01 Odyssey (M01) High Gain Antenna (HGA) Inner and Outer gimbal frames for the extended phase of the mission.

m01_sa_ext[0-9]{2}.bc.description: This file contains orientation and angular rate data for the Mars'01 Odyssey (M01) High Solar Array (SA) Inner and Outer gimbal frames for the extended phase of the mission.

m01_sc_ext[0-9]{2}.bc.description: This file contains orientation and angular velocity data for the Mars-01 Odyssey (M01) spacecraft frame, 'M01_SPACECRAFT', relative to the 'MARSIAU' inertial frame.

m01_sc_ext[0-9]{2}_rec_nadir.bc.description: This file contains predicted nominal nadir-pointed orientation for the Mars'01 Odyssey (M01) spacecraft. Refer to the file's internal comments for details regarding intended usage of this CK.

m01_ext[0-9]{2}.bsp.description: This file contains final merged ephemeris data for the 2001 Mars Odyssey (M01) spacecraft during the extended mission phase.

m01_ext[0-9]{2}_ipng_mgs95j.bsp.description: This file contains ephemeris data for the 2001 Mars Odyssey (M01) spacecraft for a portion of the extended mission phase. It was created by the IPNG group, JPL using the Mars Gravity Model MGS95J.
